minios-installer (2.4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add missing dependency for gir1.2-udisks-2.0 in debian control file
  * Add automatic bootloader type detection based on MiniOS image boot structure
  * Support all bootloader variants: grub-only, syslinux-grub, syslinux-native
  * Implement GRUB-only installation using pre-built boot.img and core.img files
  * Optimize disk zeroing to 2MB for efficient partition table cleanup
  * Prioritize syslinux-grub detection when both SYSLINUX and GRUB files present
  * Add French and Portuguese (Portugal) translations to language options
  * Enhance SYSLINUX configuration processing: support localized configs and
    fallback mechanisms

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Sat, 30 Aug 2025 23:39:31 +0300

minios-installer (2.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add function to extract boot file names from /proc/cmdline and enhance
    MiniOS source detection
  * Consolidate bootloader utilities and remove code duplication
  * Improve error handling in main installer
  * Add multilingual boot menu language selection in installer UI
  * Add support for multilingual GRUB configuration files
  * Fix fdisk partition activation using sfdisk for better reliability

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Sat, 16 Aug 2025 19:46:15 +0300

minios-installer (2.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Split minios-installer into libraries to improve code structure.
  * Correct and improve translation.
  * Improve project structure.
  * Add disk monitoring functionality.
  * Replace the inactive cancel button with a button to restart the
    installation.
  * Extend the Back and Continue buttons
  * Change the color of the Back and Continue buttons to better match the
    actions being performed.
  * Add disk size formatting and enhance device information display.
  * Add definition and display of disks that have mounted partitions.
  * Remove the disk on which MiniOS is currently running from the list.

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Mon, 07 Jul 2025 23:59:57 +0300

